pdc_discovery.title: We cannot assume all DOIs will have the same prefix

comments.body:
Notice that for the particular record in question [Enhancement of edge turbulence concomitant with ELM suppression during boron powder injection in EAST](https://datacommons.princeton.edu/discovery/catalog/doi-10-11578-1814960) the `pdc_describe_match` was successful because a PDC Describe match was found by ARK and therefore we didn't have to search by DOI.

Testing that the right record was imported:
* Link with DOI: https://datacommons.princeton.edu/discovery/doi/10.11578/1814960
* Resolves to: https://datacommons.princeton.edu/discovery/catalog/doi-10-11578-1814960 (this record came from PDC Describe)
